title: One-Pot Indian Chicken & Potato Curry with Flatbreads & Parsley
description: This aromatic dish features tender chicken and hearty potatoes simmered in a rich, flavourful sauce bursting with exotic spices.
Each spoonful delivers a perfect balance of heat and warmth, making it an irresistible comfort food.
